  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Filmmaking Program for Street Youth in Freetown</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The aim is for the program to last 6 months wherein vulnerable youth will be taught the art of writing stories (based either on the UN&apos;s 17 sustainable goals, or their own lived experience), and then bringing them to life in short documentary style films. Eventually, we would like to see this as a self-sustaining project, with previous participants advising the new recruits. Through this program, we hope to inspire social change, encourage creative self-expression, and promote education.</narrative>
  </description>
